'''The BK-3 is a Croatian kevlar combat helmet''' produced by Šestan-Busch, and is the standard combat helmet of the [[Croatian Armed Forces]]. It is also widely exported to many NATO and Mid-East customers. Latest issue variant has integrated side rails for lights and front NVG mount.

