'''Yokangassi Airport''' {{airport codes|NKY|FCBY}} is an airport serving the town of [[Nkayi, Congo|Nkayi]] in [[Bouenza Department]], [[Republic of the Congo]]. The runway is {{convert|3.4|km}} south of the town.
